{"tid":2013514,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"慈雲山和你唱","createTime":"2020-05-12T10:47:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T11:16:22.000Z","uid":207011,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ef00f5ab2e2a4847127f14076ac96925f2577b84","tid":2013514,"uid":207011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T10:47:20.000Z","msg":"1844 #慈雲山<br />\n<br />\n網民發起於慈雲山中心「和你唱」，防暴已到近毓華街及巴士總站的商場兩個主要出口戒備。<br />\n<br />\n包圍中心的警力未算重，估計警方以監察情況為主，有機會進入商場高調巡邏及要求聚眾離開。<br />\n<br />\n#公眾安全情報<br />\n<br />\n#慈雲山 1836 毓華街兩籠1衝停泊 防暴全落地 15+<br />\n#慈雲山 1842<br />\n毓華街2籠1衝<br />\n慈中巴士總站5籠3衝<br />\n雲華街1衝RB<br />\n#慈雲山 1840 約17藍衫響中心門口(中央球場入口)<br />\n1844 #慈雲山<br />\n<br />\n山友街坊要小心！"},{"pid":"5f2fabdc4f54ccd7fe2be22b3e3982194ec270fa","tid":2013514,"uid":207011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T10:47:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64683adb54e6e3baf59901fb0bfb2a38845d33db","tid":2013514,"uid":11382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T10:48:26.000Z","msg":"最少七架便衣警車已於慈雲山狗屋駛出，呢樣難防！"},{"pid":"ebcf619017211a90d4fdcb58f40a3b842316c9fe","tid":2013514,"uid":207011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T10:49:17.000Z","msg":"大家要小心！"},{"pid":"3cdddc07842bec3e625bdabb8629a49639c05dc3","tid":2013514,"uid":69472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T10:49:42.000Z","msg":"慈雲山啲癡線佬可唔可以出嚟咬啲黑警"},{"pid":"da243664f4fefab7607eb75fad1e36f9be380135","tid":2013514,"uid":155598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T10:49:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bbb51161a348fcbbd234c2cc8ebf8422f23cb8ef","tid":2013514,"uid":207011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T10:50:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b25805c865e3fe22d4e38bfe4c08168888c32db8","tid":2013514,"uid":124663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T10:50:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"abfdf66254faede417f53a5a2201f06cab409504","tid":2013514,"uid"